dibctl (0.5.1) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Name for test instance made smaller (bug with centos6)
  * Fix trace on --shell
  * Fix bugs with ssh module
  * Upload operation now display notification
  * Exceptions from novaclient now processed without trace
  * Now environment variables are passed to ssh during --shell (and shell command)
  * Better handling of NoIPFoundErrror
  * Flavor_id bugfix
  * Fix KeyboardInterrupt non-cleanup
  * Fix some cases of double cleanup (cleanup after cleanup)
  * Better handling of NotFoundInConfigError (regression)
  * --shell-only option has been removed in favor or shell command
  * Fix bug with ssh fixture in pytest runner

 -- George Shuklin <george.shuklin@gmail.com>  Wed, 05 Apr 2017 10:04:40 +0300

